sequenceDiagram
  participant U as Operator/Użytkownik
  participant API as API Inventory Agent
  participant D as Demand Agent
  participant DB as SQLite
  participant R as Redis inventory
  participant K as Kafka
  participant P as Pricing Agent

  U->>API: POST /order {product_id, okres_dni}
  API->>D: Pobierz prognozę popytu dla okresu
  D-->>API: predicted_demand

  API->>DB: Odczytaj inventory.current_stock
  DB-->>API: current_stock

  API->>API: Oblicz order_quantity = max(0, predicted_demand - current_stock)

  alt Zamówienie wymagane (order_quantity > 0)
    API->>DB: UPDATE inventory.current_stock
    API->>R: Zapisz order:{product_id}
    API->>K: Opublikuj inventory_updates
    K->>P: Przekaż inventory_updates
    P->>DB: UPDATE inventory.price
    P->>K: Opublikuj price_updates
  else Brak zamówienia (order_quantity = 0)
    API->>R: Zapisz order:{product_id} (bez zmian stanu)
  end

  API-->>U: 200 OK {product_id, current_stock, predicted_demand, order_quantity, projected_stock}
